    "title": "此処に誓うは",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "メジロアルダンの最初の3年間が\nついに終わりを迎え――",
            "enText": "The first three years of Mejiro Ardan's life \nhave finally come to an end.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "pathId": -2126673629811373255,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "“今”の彼女は、時代の中心に立ち、\n歴史の最先端を築く存在だ。",
            "enText": "In the present, she stands at the center of \nthe times and is at the forefront of history.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "pathId": 7563600726308212806,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして彼女の歩みは、\n愛すべきライバルがいる限り、\n果てしなく続いていく。",
            "enText": "And her journey will continue as long as her \nbeloved rivals are around.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "pathId": -5437899590280887642,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "人々は、彼女のその蹄跡の中に、\r\n輝きの大河を見るだろう――",
            "enText": "They will see in her hoofprints a mighty \nriver of radiance.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "pathId": -4523934880947895539,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "――少しお付き合い願えないでしょうか。",
            "enText": "―I am wondering if you could \nhelp me out a little bit.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6813712411666954380
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 4849994127111264690
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9049944228925258797,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "休日に現れるなり、メジロアルダンは\n真っ直ぐにこちらを見つめながら\n突然そう言い放った……。",
            "enText": "As soon as she appeared on her day off, \nMejiro Aldan looked straight at us and \nsuddenly said: ……",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いいけど、どこに？",
                    "enText": "Okay, but where?",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": 7530447665329284979
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": -1322430625477543244
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7153913840730438157,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "それは秘密です。",
            "enText": "It is a secret.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 27,
                    "pathId": -1340595556407966753
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -3113197456633916820
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9188596586519929974,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "車を外に用意してありますので、\nトレーナーさんの準備ができたら\n出てきてくださいね。",
            "enText": "We have a car outside, so please come out \nwhen your trainer is ready.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 9072828226107378468
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 6047346866763191993
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6359182970201750272,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "何が何だかよくわからないが、\r\n慌てて外出の準備をして\nメジロアルダンに同行することにした。",
            "enText": "Not quite sure what was going on, I hurriedly \nprepared to go out and accompany Mejiro Ardan.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": 6630882838530200606
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": -1090342320122131321
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1262952755986155747,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "――ここはいつ来ても見晴らしがよくて、\r\n落ち着く場所ですね。",
            "enText": "―I always feel at home here, \nwith the great view.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 49,
                    "pathId": 7309055158986300887
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -1050302828022550436
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5007284754986315480,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "メジロアルダンのばあやさんが運転する車に\r\nより連れてこられた場所は、メジロ家の\n保養所の近くにある高台だった。",
            "enText": "The place where we were taken by the car \ndriven by Aldan's grandmother was on a \nhilltop near the family's recreation center. \nThe place where we were taken by the car \ndriven by the grandmother of Mejiro Aldan was \non a hill near the recreation center.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -5697714302095089883
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -7960106117908413399
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5365810159524103796,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさん。\nここがどこだか、覚えていますか？",
            "enText": "Trainer. Do you remember where you are?",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君にロードマップを見せた場所だな",
                    "enText": "That's where I showed you the roadmap.",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方にロードマップを見せた場所だね",
                    "enText": "This is where I showed you the roadmap.",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 3240516408439737407
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -5588069937486257104
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8683945125832901058,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "はい。トレーナーさんが初めて\n私に“未来”を示してくれた場所で――",
            "enText": "Yes. It was there that my trainer first \nshowed me my future.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 318353383430386852
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -3756201391631275754
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7200925125671579121,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "“今”の私の、原点です。",
            "enText": "This is the starting point \nof my \"present\" life.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 1922279604207065257
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -1274910640405795418
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -2557834721640387868
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2449101149613990221,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ばあや",
            "enName": "Elderly Maid",
            "jpText": "お嬢様。準備ができましたので、\nこちらに広げさせていただきます。",
            "enText": "Miss. We are ready and will \nspread it out over here.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -3682850813952050009
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": 2442936395592730011
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 7494012918257443380
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 669238279082386795,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ありがとう、ばあや。",
            "enText": "Thanks, Baya.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "一体なにをするんだ？",
                    "enText": "What the hell are you doing?",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "一体なにをするの？",
                    "enText": "What the hell are you doing?",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 44,
                    "pathId": -6793851741956801203
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -2329960679752494620
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2265845276919295606,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ここで、トレーナーさんの絵を\n私に描かせていただけないでしょうか。",
            "enText": "I wonder if you would allow me to paint a \npicture of your trainer here.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "絵？",
                    "enText": "Painting?",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": -2090677863941639881
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -797355624657567398
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3477544944493643938,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "はい、絵です。",
            "enText": "Yes, it is a picture.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 7728401742145811334
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -3413876628175687683
                }
