            "pathId": -1600173729285265835,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "……この3年間、トレーナーさんと共に\n道を歩んできて、私は様々なものを\nトレーナーさんからもらってきました。",
            "enText": "…… I have been on the road with my trainer \nfor the past three years and I have received \nmany things from her. I have received many \nthings from my trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": 7844005919999388488
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -1077639292787312942
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -8722856386303147765
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8824527089289717603,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "どれも大事な、なにひとつ零したくない\n思い出ばかりで……――",
            "enText": "They are all precious memories that I don't \nwant to lose any of. ……―",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -3650771453651998040
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -4013123123564366475
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 3756398964436447175
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8057337028509139721,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "気づけば、もっとトレーナーさんとの時間を\n形に残せないかと思うようになったんです。",
            "enText": "I found myself wondering if I could \npreserve more of my time with the \ntrainer in a tangible way.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -3157696256224661205
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -8712679694987305374
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2999372540586707527,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "それで思いついたのが……\n入院中に嗜んでいた絵でした。",
            "enText": "So I came up with…… a painting that I had \nenjoyed while in the hospital.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -1506426185866314298
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -8153437983061388380
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8172044438003559129,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ここでトレーナーさんに\n“未来”を示してもらった時の、\nあの気持ち。",
            "enText": "I remember that feeling I had when the \ntrainer showed me the \"future\" here.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -1640095055111066787
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 9019842713940017558
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5289530068833018040,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "そして“今”ここにある私の気持ち。",
            "enText": "And how I feel here \"now\".",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -7103994336641777536
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": 8847171784676681816
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -2994432512330512971
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3854862846046642914,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "それをこの場所で、\n絵に残したいのです。",
            "enText": "I want to leave a picture of it here.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -5263518198958508944
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 353591746417287605
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -2684984301095359872
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4183537228490587315,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "どうか……私のわがままを、\n聞いてもらえないでしょうか。",
            "enText": "Please…… will you listen to my selfishness?",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "とりあえず、ポーズを取ればいいのかな",
                    "enText": "I guess I'll just have to pose for now.",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -6553914054121720644
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": 1372482128736583413
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8949873196480256514,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "――――",
            "enText": "――",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -7091139857891064517
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -4282535910641438656
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7020082998368881354,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "描いても、いいのですか？",
            "enText": "Can I draw it, if I want to?",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "当然だよ",
                    "enText": "Of course.",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": 2313697844673347503
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 7683286976571018160
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -291365279040457216,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "メジロアルダンが、\r\n“今”1番したいことを、大事にする。",
            "enText": "Mejiro Aldan values what she \nwants to do most \"now\".",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 133414060178268499
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -3488436885199195498
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6541986976924176207,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "それが……この3年間で自分が\r\n覚悟をもって取り組んだことの1つだ。\n今更なにを断ることがあるだろうか。",
            "enText": "That's one of the things I've…… been prepared \nto do over the past three years. What is \nthere to say no to now?",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺は、君のトレーナーだから",
                    "enText": "I'm your trainer.",
                    "nextBlock": 31
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私は、貴方のトレーナーだから",
                    "enText": "I'm your trainer.",
                    "nextBlock": 31
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 123,
                    "pathId": -6519815401691769295
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 123,
                    "pathId": -8179205079633642715
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1139746772647704636,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "…………ありがとうございます。",
            "enText": "Thank you …………",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 2536516434619566109
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": -4628505460919903976
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 679774899673299647,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "その言葉に私は、\n今日まで何度励まされたんでしょうね……。",
            "enText": "How many times have those words encouraged me \nto this day? ……",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": 2721531806446585882
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -4933799670028183845
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8408651200119200785,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "――っ、そうだ。",
            "enText": "― Yes, that's right.",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": -8604488206737137248
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 1716512866921222212
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6340813171176781915,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "せっかくですし、\r\nトレーナーさんも描いてみませんか？",
            "enText": "Why don't you draw a trainer, too?",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えっ",
                    "enText": "What's up?",
                    "nextBlock": 35
                }
